Regina, Saskatchewan S4S 0B1 Tel: (306) 787-2290 E-mail: careers@legassembly.sk.ca Please quote competition 1047432 in the subject of your email. Clearly indicate in your resume or cover letter where and how you have gained the required knowledge and qualifications. Selections for interviews will be based on this information. Thank you for your interest in the Legislative Assembly Service. Only candidates selected for interview will be contacted Compensation $5,825 to $7,574 per month Closes: 12 May, 2023 Legislative Assembly of Saskatchewan Regina , SK Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
