e in the form of a resume with an accompanying letter detailing your experience and qualifications relative to this position.We thank all applicants in advance for their submissions; however, only those candidates selected for an interview will receive a response.Bernice Crowe, Manager of Human ResourcesCariboo Regional DistrictSuite D, 180 3rd Avenue NWilliams Lake, BC V2G 2A4Email: mailbox@cariboord.ca Compensation $30.41 per hour Closes: 11 June, 2023 Cariboo Regional District Williams Lake , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
